overview.en: Bullion Exchange provides an effective real-time, good supportive, responsive cryptocurrency exchange, it enables users to trade continuously without waiting for transactions to mine, fill multiple orders at once, and cancel orders anytime without any charge.
overview.cn: Bullion Exchange提供了有效的實時，良好的支持性，響應性的加密貨幣交換，它使用戶能夠連續交易而無需等待交易挖掘，一次完成多個訂單以及隨時取消訂單而無需任何費用。
